00:29:07,116 --> 00:29:10,079
And then sometimes they'll execute on those things less

518
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:11,821
less than appropriately

519
00:29:12,732 --> 00:29:17,579
And I'm really hopeful that the industry will be taking these as learning experiences.

