00:29:44,747 --> 00:29:48,230
that we will get there, although I also feel very strongly

527
00:29:48,270 --> 00:29:52,093
that we are not there, and that we are not doing

528
00:29:52,333 --> 00:29:55,575
as good a job as we can be representing various cultures

529
00:29:55,615 --> 00:29:57,376
and identities and yeah.

