00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:18,070
Yeah, I mean, I guess some of it's just...

535
00:30:19,171 --> 00:30:21,351
I know sometimes going to board game conventions,

536
00:30:21,411 --> 00:30:23,252
I walk into a room and it's just full...

