00:31:29,331 --> 00:31:33,193
We are, you know, there are people who are doing a lot of work trying to foster

555
00:31:33,353 --> 00:31:34,514
more inclusive behavior among

556
00:31:35,134 --> 00:31:38,096
players which will lead into more inclusive behavior among, you know, within

557
00:31:38,256 --> 00:31:39,877
the design scene as we get more people

558
00:31:40,217 --> 00:31:41,758
who are enthusiastic about games in general.

