00:32:05,776 --> 00:32:10,440
But, yeah, I think there are barriers to entry that companies are working on,

566
00:32:11,541 --> 00:32:14,043
and that we as a culture are...

567
00:32:15,633 --> 00:32:19,475
Struggling with and it will take time and it will take people who are in positions of power

568
00:32:22,257 --> 00:32:25,258
Making active decisions and making choices that are like, okay

569
00:32:25,278 --> 00:32:26,519
Let's see

570
00:32:26,879 --> 00:32:31,342
I want more marginalized voices in my game where I think this game would be more interesting if

571
00:32:31,382 --> 00:32:37,505
We can have like this culture represented accurately and we can serve like this either community or this, you know

572
00:32:37,985 --> 00:32:44,269
present this thing that we don't see often effectively and that will usually require a more diverse set of creators like that is

573
00:32:45,359 --> 00:32:51,062
I think, you know, we live in a capitalist society, and currently, diversity is kind

