00:34:25,125 --> 00:34:31,010
They feel a lot more inclusive in terms of the range of games that they supply to people

599
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:34,432
and then the sort of events that they throw.

600
00:34:35,373 --> 00:34:38,836
Some of them I think, I mean, the tabletop industry is very broad

