00:34:38,876 --> 00:34:44,820
and it feels like there should be more cafes that are across that broad ability.

602
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:49,244
So there's some that are for more hardcore people who want to be playing Key Forge or whatever it is,

603
00:34:49,564 --> 00:34:53,827
but then there's some who just want to play with their kids and more casual games.

604
00:34:53,847 --> 00:34:54,508
I would love to see.

605
00:34:55,048 --> 00:34:57,329
you know, them specializing a bit more.

