00:35:02,892 --> 00:35:06,994
experience, anecdotal evidence, Quirkle had

608
00:35:07,114 --> 00:35:11,336
a really unique experience in terms of contacting digital media

609
00:35:14,078 --> 00:35:14,358
and

610
00:35:14,918 --> 00:35:18,981
board game cafes. My husband Chris was really good at sending

611
00:35:19,021 --> 00:35:22,923
out copies of Quirkle when it first came out. And he sent one to W. Eric Martin who at that point

612
00:35:22,963 --> 00:35:24,183
was running Board Game News.

