00:35:59,358 --> 00:36:02,739
So for me, and then Quirkle went on to win the Spiel des Jahres,

629
00:36:02,779 --> 00:36:05,099
so for me, board game cafes, super important,

630
00:36:05,159 --> 00:36:08,840
and reaching out to different forms of media

631
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,960
and letting them know about your game, super important.

632
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:12,921
That led very directly to...

633
00:36:13,561 --> 00:36:15,543
to the publisher Quirkle ended up with in Germany.

634
00:36:16,423 --> 00:36:20,226
And also, I think in that case, Quirkle

635
00:36:20,266 --> 00:36:22,588
found a stronger foothold among gamers

636
00:36:23,309 --> 00:36:25,290
because we did that outreach than we expected.

